    "# 92. The Location-Routing Problem (LRP)\n",
    "## Tier 7: The Human-AI Symbiotic Partnership (The Centaur Model)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key assumptions\n",
    "- Human-AI collaboration combines domain expertise with computational power\n",
    "- AI proposes multiple diverse solutions with explainable reasoning\n",
    "- Human provides strategic insights and qualitative constraints\n",
    "- Explainable AI (XAI) makes AI decisions transparent and understandable\n",
    "- Iterative refinement loop improves solutions through human feedback\n",
    "\n",
    "### Approach (step-by-step)\n",
    "1. **AI Proposal Generation**: Create multiple high-quality, diverse solutions\n",
    "2. **Explainable AI Interface**: Provide transparent reasoning for each solution\n",
    "3. **Human Evaluation**: Human planner reviews and provides qualitative feedback\n",
    "4. **Constraint Integration**: Human inputs (no-go zones, strategic preferences) are incorporated\n",
    "5. **Iterative Refinement**: AI refines solutions based on human guidance\n",
    "6. **Joint Decision Making**: Final solution co-created by human and AI\n",
    "\n",
    "### What to look for in the results\n",
    "- Multiple solution alternatives with different strategic objectives\n",
    "- Explainable AI reasoning showing why each solution was chosen\n",
    "- Human-AI interaction patterns and learning loops\n",
    "- Impact of human constraints on solution quality\n",
    "- Comparison of human-AI solutions vs pure AI solutions\n",
    "\n",
    "### Concrete example (from the source)\n",
    "- **Problem**: Same 2-depot, 3-customer instance with human-AI collaboration\n",
    "- **AI Solutions**: Minimum-cost, minimum-carbon, maximum-resilience portfolios\n",
    "- **Human Input**: No-go zone for depot due to zoning law changes\n",
    "- **Expected Outcome**: Superior solution combining AI optimization with human strategic insight"
   ]
  },
